01:35.679 --> 01:37.848
It's 95 degrees outside.

01:37.890 --> 01:39.767
It's 110 in here.

01:39.808 --> 01:41.142
We have to run the heater

01:41.184 --> 01:43.228
so the radiator

01:41.184 --> 01:43.228
doesn't boil over.

01:43.270 --> 01:44.813
Hal, stop swerving.

01:44.855 --> 01:46.941
This darn silver Toyota's

01:44.855 --> 01:46.941
been tailgating me

01:46.982 --> 01:48.149
for the last three miles.

01:48.191 --> 01:50.110
Just pull over,

01:48.191 --> 01:50.110
let him pass.

01:51.570 --> 01:53.154
Oh, flashing

01:51.570 --> 01:53.154
the brights.

01:53.196 --> 01:55.156
It's going to be

01:53.196 --> 01:55.156
like that, huh?

01:55.198 --> 01:56.157
(tires screeching)

01:56.199 --> 01:57.242
Huh!

01:57.284 --> 01:59.954
Good lord, Hal,

01:57.284 --> 01:59.954
he could have a gun.

01:59.995 --> 02:01.622
Just let him pass.

02:01.663 --> 02:05.125
All right, silver Toyota,

02:01.663 --> 02:05.125
you win this round.

02:06.919 --> 02:10.089
Go ahead, get there

02:06.919 --> 02:10.089
two seconds sooner!

02:10.130 --> 02:13.008
That guy is just an accident

02:10.130 --> 02:13.008
waiting to happen.

02:13.050 --> 02:13.968
