02:24.227 --> 02:26.229
(chuckles) It's a good

02:24.227 --> 02:26.229
thing I found you.

02:26.271 --> 02:28.899
It's not very safe

02:26.271 --> 02:28.899
for a little boy like you

02:28.941 --> 02:30.191
to be all by yourself.

02:30.233 --> 02:32.027
